title: Bobby May End Radio Career To Go Into Politics + Thomas Rhett Tells Bobby He Dared Wife To Kiss Him Before They Started Dating

description:
Bobby talks about wrapping up his radio career at the end of his current contract. Thomas Rhett stops by for the Friday Morning Conversation and talks about daring his wife to kiss him to see if they could work as a couple. Also, Amy saw something she felt was inappropriate at the pool she takes her kids to.
